Usage: FORMAT WALLOPS <format description>
  Controls how wallops appear

  Valid format characters:
       F          Nick of oper sending wallops
       M          The message
       O          Replaced by "*" if person sending wallops is an operator

See Also:  
  WALLOPS
  OPERWALL
